# gen78: module activation tracking. The dispatch loop stores which module
# claimed each turn, so "which part of you answered that?" reads real state.
> who are you?
< I am parrot0.
> which part of you answered that?
< The 'self' module answered your last question.
> what is 2 + 2
< 4.
> what module handled that?
< The 'arith' module answered your last question.
# A not-understood fallback is tracked too.
> zxcvbnm qwerty
< I don't understand that yet.
> which part of you answered that?
< No module could handle that — it fell through to the not-understood fallback.
# Italian cues.
> chi sei?
< I am parrot0.
> quale modulo ha risposto?
< The 'self' module answered your last question.
